'''日產汽車訴尼桑電腦案'''（Nissan Motors v. Nissan Computer）是[[美國|美國]]一宗涉兩間公司的名稱及[[互聯網|互聯網]][[域名|域名]]「nissan.com」官司<ref name='Anderson 2001-01-03'>{{cite news | first = Mark K. | last = Anderson | title = Who Gets to Drive Nissan.com? | date = 2001-01-03 | url = http://archive.wired.com/politics/law/news/2001/01/40939?currentPage=all | work = Wired | access-date = 2014-02-11 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003411/http://archive.wired.com/politics/law/news/2001/01/40939?currentPage=all | dead-url = no }}</ref>，因持續時間長而在美國多地受廣泛注意<ref name='Leonard 2002-06-03'>{{cite news | first = Andrew | last = Leonard | title = Nissan vs. Nissan | date = 2002-06-03 | url = http://www.salon.com/2002/06/03/nissan/ | work = Salon | access-date = 2014-02-11 | archive-date = 2021-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210529214146/https://www.salon.com/2002/06/03/nissan/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Nissan vs. Nissan |work=IEEE Spectrum Careers |url=http://www.spectrum.ieee.org/careers/careerstemplate.jsp?ArticleId=i100302 |access-date=2006-05-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20051202010152/http://www.spectrum.ieee.org/careers/careerstemplate.jsp?ArticleId=i100302 <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archive-date= 2005-12-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Nissan Motor Co. v. Nissan Computer Corp., and the Evolving Law of Trademark Dilution on the Internet |work=TrademarkDilution.com |url=http://www.lctjournal.washington.edu/Vol2/a002Rozsnyai.html |access-date=2006-05-24 |archive-date=2006-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060703180016/http://www.lctjournal.washington.edu/Vol2/a002Rozsnyai.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==事件背景==
===日產汽車===
在1970年代後期，汽車製造廠商[[達特桑|Datsun]]（[[日產汽車|日產汽車]]的附屬品牌）開始逐步為在美銷售的汽車上，貼上「Nissan」及「Datsun by Nissan」廠徽，並最終在1,100多間代理商中完成這項品牌變更。至1981年秋季，Datsun宣布其在美國的名稱將會更改<ref>Aaker, David A. ''Managing Brand Equity : Capitalizing on the Value of a Brand Name'', New York: The Free Press, 1991 {{ISBN|0-02-900101-3}} Chapter 3, Pg. 57</ref>。在1982至1986年間把公司口號「Datsun, We Are Driven!」過渡至「The Name is Nissan」<ref name='ZCCA'>[http://www.zcca.org/pages/ZCarsZhistoryDatsuntoNissan.htm What's in a name?] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060508085037/http://www.zcca.org/pages/ZCarsZhistoryDatsuntoNissan.htm |date=8 May 2006 }} - ZCCA</ref>。在公司完成名稱變更計劃五年後，其出產的汽車在部分出口市場仍同時貼上「Datsun」及「Nissan」廠徽，「Datsun」的知名度仍然高於「Nissan」<ref name='ZCCA'/><ref name='Aaker'>Aaker, David A. ''Managing Brand Equity : Capitalizing on the Value of a Brand Name'', New York: The Free Press, 1991 {{ISBN|0-02-900101-3}} Chapter 3, Pg. 56</ref>。

===尼桑電腦===
1980年，[[以色列|以色列]]移民烏茲·尼桑（Uzi Nissan）在北卡羅來納州羅利市創辦汽車服務公司「Nissan Foreign Car」<ref name='UN NFC'>{{cite web | url = http://www.digest.com/Nissan_Foreign_Car.htm | title = Nissan Foreign Car | access-date = 2014-02-11 | last = Nissan | first = Uzi | work = Digest.com | archive-date = 2021-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210529214145/https://www.digest.com/Nissan_Foreign_Car.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name='UN main'>{{cite web | url = http://www.digest.com/Big_Story.php | title = Nissan Motor vs. Nissan Computer | access-date = 2014-02-11 | last = Nissan | first = Uzi | work = Digest.com}}</ref>。1987年，尼桑創辦進出口貿易公司「Nissan International, Ltd.」，產品以重型設備及電腦為主<ref name='UN NI'>{{cite web | url = http://www.digest.com/NIL.htm | title = Nissan International | access-date = 2014-02-11 | last = Nissan | first = Uzi | work = Digest.com}}</ref>。至1991年，尼桑創辦電腦公司「Nissan Computer Corporation」，公司從事個人電腦、伺服器及電腦零件銷售及服務，其後亦開始經營互聯網服務及開發。尼桑電腦於1994年6月4日註冊域名「nissan.com」，該域名於五年後方為日產汽車所注意<ref name='UN main'/><ref name='Anderson 2001-01-03'/>。

尼桑本人於2020年7月因確診[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]病逝<ref name="jalopnik2020">{{cite web |last1=Westbrook |first1=Justin T. |title=Uzi Nissan, Internet Domain Owner Who Fought Nissan in Court for a Decade, Has Died of Covid-19 |url=https://jalopnik.com/uzi-nissan-internet-domain-owner-who-fought-nissan-in-1844535615 |website=[[Jalopnik|Jalopnik]] |publisher=G/O Media Group |access-date=27 December 2020 |date=28 July 2020 |archive-date=2021-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903155843/https://jalopnik.com/uzi-nissan-internet-domain-owner-who-fought-nissan-in-1844535615 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Uzi Nissan, organized by Erez Halfon|url=https://www.gofundme.com/f/Uzi-Nissan|accessdate=2021-04-29|work=gofundme.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430121859/https://www.gofundme.com/f/Uzi-Nissan|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Man Who Fought Nissan Over a Website—And Won—Has Died of COVID-19|url=https://www.thedrive.com/news/35179/the-man-who-fought-nissan-over-a-website-and-won-has-died-of-covid-19|accessdate=2021-04-29|last=Gilboy|first=James|work=The Drive|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104223654/https://www.thedrive.com/news/35179/the-man-who-fought-nissan-over-a-website-and-won-has-died-of-covid-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==案件==
日產汽車認為尼桑電腦所使用的名稱構成[[商標淡化|商標淡化]]，指控尼桑[[域名搶注|搶先註冊域名]]，並要求出讓域名。然而尼桑電腦乃以創辦人Uzi Nissan的姓氏命名<ref>{{cite web |title=Nissan Motor vs. Nissan Computer |work=citizen.org |url=http://www.citizen.org/documents/CourtofAppealsRulingNissanMotorvNissanComputer.pdf |access-date=2012-05-26 |archive-date=2011-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110101234423/http://www.citizen.org/documents/CourtofAppealsRulingNissanMotorvNissanComputer.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name='2011-04-09 Yale'>{{cite news | first = Daniel | last = A. | title = Why Nissan.com Isn't a Car Website | date = 2011-04-09 | url = https://yalelawtech.org/2011/04/09/why-nissan-com-isnt-a-car-website/ | work = Yale Law & Technology | access-date = 2014-02-11 | archive-date = 2021-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210529214146/https://yalelawtech.org/2011/04/09/why-nissan-com-isnt-a-car-website/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Nissan Motor vs. Nissan Computer |work=Nissan Computer Corporation |url=http://www.nissan.com/Digest/The_Story.php |access-date=2006-05-24 |archive-date=2021-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210529214204/https://www.nissan.com/Digest/The_Story.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在案件判決後，日產汽車使用「www.nissanusa.com」作為美國地區網頁的域名<ref name='Nissan USA'>{{cite web | url = https://www.nissanusa.com/ | title = Nissan USA | access-date = 2014-02-11 | archive-date = 2020-12-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201220141410/https://www.nissanusa.com/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>
。

